# Frontend — UX/UI standards

Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS in `ygo_app/static/`. Follow existing patterns in `app.js`, `index.html`, `style.css` before inventing new ones.

## Design system

- CSS variables from `:root`: `--bg`, `--surface`, `--accent`, `--muted`, `--radius`, `--danger`.
- Reuse classes: `.tab`, `.secondary`, `.hidden`, `.filter-group--compact`, `.modal-overlay`, `.icon-btn`, `.empty-msg`, `.supplement-icon-btn`.
- Dark theme; `color-scheme: dark` in `index.html`. Responsive: `viewport` meta, flex/wrap, no mobile-breaking fixed widths.

## Accessibility

- Tabs/panels: `role="tablist"` / `tab` / `tabpanel`, `aria-selected`, `aria-controls`, `hidden`, `tabindex`.
- Modals: `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal`, `aria-labelledby`; Escape closes topmost; focus `#modal-close` on card open.
- Icon-only: `aria-label` (+ `data-tooltip` on `.supplement-icon-btn`). Live/async: `#auth-error`, `#auth-checking`, `aria-busy`.
- Semantic HTML (`button`, `label`+`for`); `:focus-visible` on interactive controls.

## Loading & perceived speed

- Immediate feedback: `renderModalSkeleton`, `#import-progress`, `setButtonBusy`, `.loading-spinner`, `runModalAction`.
- Card modal: open overlay first; seed preview (`findModalSeed`); disable actions until API load completes.
- Stale guards: `*RequestSeq` before fetch; ignore outdated responses. Performance: event delegation, tab caches, lazy `cardImgTag`.

## Empty, error & feedback

- Empty states: `.empty-msg`, `renderSupplementEmpty` — never blank panels or silent failures.
- Errors: `showToast` + inline `#auth-error`; avoid `alert()` for routine API failures.
- Destructive/replace: `confirm()` before delete, preset delete, CSV import with `replace=true`.

## Modals, navigation & state

- Card modal: reset supplements, tag chips, and **uncommitted** `#tag-input` on open/switch/close — no draft carry-over.
- Hash routing: `syncRouteHash` + `{ fromRouter: true }`; card route is overlay — do **not** switch background tab to Search.
- Avoid double loads: `lastAppliedRouteHash`, `tabRouteAlreadyApplied`, `suppressHashSync`. Modal close: `history.back()` only with in-app history; else `replace`. Update `document.title`.

## Forms & auth

- Tabbed Sign in / Create account; `#auth-checking` while validating token (no login flash for returning users).
- `validatePasswordStrength()` before register; hint sync with `ygo_app/auth.py`; `autocomplete`; accent primary submit.

## Content & display

- Search tiles compact (name + type). Metadata strip must not duplicate description or summoning condition.
- Tags: removable chips (`aria-label` on remove), `#filter-tag` + `#tag-datalist`, chip click → tag search.
- Errata/tips: icon-only buttons; explicit empty copy in supplement popups.
- **Sanitized HTML only:** errata `lore_html` (server-sanitized) is the routine `innerHTML` exception; else `textContent` / `escapeHtml()`.

## Security & conventions

- JWT in `localStorage` — treat DOM injection as high impact. Never sync secrets into URL hash; allowlist `ROUTE_SEARCH_KEYS`, cap param length/count.
- Bump `?v=` on edited `<link>` / `<script>` in `index.html`.

## Examples

```
BAD:  el.innerHTML = card.name
GOOD: el.textContent = card.name
BAD:  Tag draft persists when opening another card
GOOD: Clear #tag-input in renderModalSkeleton and closeCardModalOverlay
BAD:  alert(err.message) on login failure
GOOD: showAuthError + showToast(..., { variant: "error" })
BAD:  switchView("search") behind #/card/{id} from Collection
GOOD: openCardModal(id, { fromRouter: true }) — background tab unchanged
```
